<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>인천상공회의소 교육 신청</title>
    <script src="https://js.tosspayments.com/v1/payment"></script>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; padding: 20px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        h1 { color: #0056b3; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        select { width: 100%; padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; }
        button {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        button:hover { background-color: #004494; }
        .price-display { font-size: 20px; margin-top: 10px; font-weight: bold; color: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>인천상공회의소 교육 신청</h1>
    <p>원하시는 교육 과정을 선택하고 결제해 주세요.</p>
    
    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="course">교육 과정 선택</label>
        <select id="course" onchange="updatePrice()">
            <option value="course1" data-price="50000">스마트 팩토리 기초 과정 (50,000원)</option>
            <option value="course2" data-price="100000">AI 데이터 분석 실무 (100,000원)</option>
            <option value="course3" data-price="30000">비즈니스 영어 회화 (30,000원)</option>
            <option value="course4" data-price="150000">경영 지도사 자격 반 (150,000원)</option>
        </select>
        <div id="price-display" class="price-display">결제 금액: 50,000원</div>
    </div>

    <button onclick="pay()">결제하기</button>

    <script>
        const clientKey = '<%= clientKey %>';
        const tossPayments = TossPayments(clientKey);

        function updatePrice() {
            const select = document.getElementById('course');
            const price = select.options[select.selectedIndex].getAttribute('data-price');
            document.getElementById('price-display').innerText = '결제 금액: ' + Number(price).toLocaleString() + '원';
        }

        function pay() {
            const select = document.getElementById('course');
            const selectedOption = select.options[select.selectedIndex];
            const amount = Number(selectedOption.getAttribute('data-price'));
            const orderName = selectedOption.text.split('(')[0].trim(); // Extract name part
            
            // Unique Order ID per attempt
            const orderId = '<%= orderId %>_' + Date.now();

            tossPayments.requestPayment('카드', {
                amount: amount,
                orderId: orderId,
                orderName: orderName,
                customerName: '교육생', // In a real app, collect this from an input
                successUrl: window.location.origin + '/success',
                failUrl: window.location.origin + '/fail',
            }).catch(function (error) {
                if (error.code === 'USER_CANCEL') {
                    // User canceled
                } else {
                    alert(error.message);
                }
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
